         Bigraph Evaluator & Rewriting

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

REQUIREMENTS:

  *  OCaml >=3.10
  *  findlib
  *  ocamlbuild
  *  CamlMiniSat
  *  Graphviz

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL:

  > ./build install 
 
  Override variable INSTDIR (default /usr/bin) to install BigraphER in a
  different directory. Note that superuser privileges may be required.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

UNINSTALL:

  > ./build uninstall

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
